As a part of ICONS 2 (Integrated Scientific Communication), we were asked to write an independent research report of potential ideas and pitch it to a class of 20 students. 
The pitch was supposed to attract students to an idea and form groups. My pitch of smart-grid technology ended up attracting 5 students and being chosen as one of the 5 final projects for ICONS 2. 
